<arggraph id="micro_c108" topic_id="composting_helps_environment" stance="pro">
  <edu id="e1"><![CDATA[Composting can help the environment]]></edu>
  <edu id="e2"><![CDATA[because composting reduces greenhouse gases.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e3"><![CDATA[Composting also helps to replenish soil with critical minerals and nutrients that lead to better soil quality.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e4"><![CDATA[Another benefit of composting is that it helps to keep food scraps out of landfills.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e5"><![CDATA[There can be a downside with composting due to runoff]]></edu>
  <edu id="e6"><![CDATA[as some composting materials contain heavy metals]]></edu>
  <edu id="e7"><![CDATA[but enhanced filtration systems are minimizing the risk of this impact.]]></edu>
  <edu id="e8"><![CDATA[Overall, composting has multiple benefits that will all contribute in aggregate toward helping our environment.]]></edu>
